title: MAGIX Movie Edit Pro 2019 18.0.1.207 (x64) Premium Edition Full
description:
[img]http://babupc.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/MAGIX-Movie-Edit-Pro-1.gif[/img]


Movie Edit Pro Premium will allow you to fill the videos with additional positive energy. Even without considerable experience in working with video, you can turn on the present, creating real masterpieces of the level of the best world analogues.

With up to 1,500 intros/outros, transitions, movie templates, music and sound effect, the new selection is bigger than ever before. And, as your creative demands grow with each video project, the effects will grow with you! Find new, additional effects in the integrated Store.

From effects specialists like NewBlue and HitFilm, the best plug-ins such as picture-in-picture effects, split screens, color correction and audio optimization, are available now at an exclusive price in the new in-app Store!

Main functions:
• Convenient control: a well thought-out interface with precise adjustments
• Accelerated processing: unique performance thanks to 64-bit architecture support
• Edge-to-frame installation: on 99 multimedia tracks
• 4K proxy editing: allows video playback without jumps and delays
• Multi-camera editing: simultaneously work with 4 cameras
• Secondary color correction: processing of individual color shades
• All for creative work: special effects, transitions, intro / endings and much more
• On the road: the ability to start video projects using the Movie Edit Touch application

All that is in the version Plus, and much more. Thanks to this software product, any footage shot on vacation will become a real high-grade hit
